fields.name: Health Insurance
fields.description: Covers medical costs in case of hospitalisation

fields.name: Travel Insurance
fields.description: This covers medical costs while travelling

fields.name: Personal Accident
fields.description: Pays lumpsum in case of an accident

fields.name: Critical Illness
fields.description: Pays a lumpsum on detection of a major critical disease like cancer

fields.name: Cancer Cover
fields.description: Pays lumpsum on detection of cancer and stages

fields.name: Term Life Insurance
fields.description: Pays cover amount in case of death

fields.name: Royal Sundaram General Insurance Co. Limited
Activ Assure Diamond Super NCB + Unlimited Reload
Hospital Coverage
fields.long_description: Number of Hospitals with cashless facility

fields.name: Day Care Procedures
fields.long_description: Day Care Treatment refers to medical treatment and/or surgical procedure which is Undertaken under General or Local Anaesthesia in hospital / day care centre in less than 24 hours because of technological advancements, and Which would have otherwise required a hospitalisation of more than 24 hours.

fields.name: Pre Policy Checkups
fields.long_description: Some plans do not ask for a pre-policy medical checkup

fields.name: Pre Hospitalisation Expenses
fields.long_description: Pre hospitalization expenses cover the medical expenses required for incidental health examination and tests that occur prior to hospitalization. It indicates number of days for which medical expenses are admissible.

fields.name: Post Hospitalisation Expenses
fields.long_description: Post hospitalization expenses cover the required medical expenses that might occur after the hospitalization. Number of days shows time period for which such expenses are admissible.

fields.name: Hospital Room eligibility
fields.long_description: Room Rent Limit is a Limit applied by Insurance Cos on the the choice of Hospital Room you can opt for. The limit could be on the Room Charges or on the Room Category. The lesser the cappings the better.

fields.name: No Claim Bonus
fields.long_description: Most plans increase your cover for each year of no claims and reduce it back in case of claims. Some plans do not reduce your cover when a claim happens

fields.name: Ambulance Charges
fields.long_description: some plans pay for ambulance charges

fields.name: Free Health Checkup
fields.long_description: some plans offer complimentary annual health checkup

fields.name: Restoration / Recharge of SI
fields.long_description: Automatic restoration of the Basic Sum Insured immediately either upon exhaustion of the Basic Sum Insured or upon admission of first claim. Restored amount can only be used for treatments other than the earlier one.

fields.name: Pre Existing Diseases
fields.long_description: Pre-Existing Diseases would include various health conditions including ones diagnosed by a doctor, any major hospitalization in the past, ailments for which one is taking medication. Such ailments are covered after certain time duration. The lower the waiting periods, the better.

fields.name: Wellness Factors
fields.long_description: some plans offer incentives, discounts on renewals and other benefits as long as you stay fit and active

fields.name: Maternity Coverage
fields.long_description: Medical Treatment Expenses traceable to childbirth (including caesarean sections). It also includes expenses towards lawful medical termination of pregnancy. Coverage is broken down into inpatient and outpatient services. Typically, inpatient coverage includes hospitalization and physician fees associated with child birth. Outpatient coverage pays for prenatal and postnatal OB-GYN office visits.

fields.name: CoPay
fields.long_description: some plans require you to pay a % of the hospital cost (10-20% usually) and pay the remaining

fields.name: Eye cover
fields.long_description: some plans cover eye surgery, opthalmologicala conditions and cost of spectacles

fields.name: Dental cover
fields.long_description: An outpatient (or out-patient) is a patient who is not hospitalized for 24 hours or more but who visits a hospital, clinic, or associated facility for diagnosis or treatment.

fields.name: AYUSH cover
fields.long_description: In case policyholders need organ transplant then the donor also needs to go for surgery which involves cost to policyholder. It shows whether expenses towards treatment of organ donor is covered or not.

fields.name: Recover Benefit
fields.long_description: Copay is your share (in %) on the final payable claim amount, that you have to bear. Insurance companies will deduct this share and then settle the claim. Lower the copay the better.

fields.name: Home Hospitalisation / Domicilliary
fields.long_description: In many cases the patient needs to be treated at home and cannot be taken to the hospital.

fields.name: Worldwide emergency Coverage
fields.long_description: some plans cover you in case of an emergency happening worldwide and evacuate you to the nearest hospital

fields.name: Family Floater Option
fields.long_description: Ayurveda, Yoga & Naturopathy, Unani, Siddha and Homoeopathy (AYUSH)

fields.name: Doctor-on-Call Service
fields.long_description: Company specific unique offer

fields.name: Critical Illness Rider
fields.long_description: Critical illnesses like Cancer / Stroke cost more. So some plans provide an additional lumpsum in case of diagnosis of a critical illness. However, you get higher and cost effective coverage, if you buy a specific critical illness or top-up plans, available separately.
